00:14:01.488 --> 00:14:03.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your people are the Skrreea.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You need our help.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:14:03.407 --> 00:14:05.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no time to waste.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:14:06.426 --> 00:14:07.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your people, where are they?</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:14:08.145 --> 00:14:10.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are on the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>creshnee</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> side of the Eye.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:10.925 --> 00:14:12.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The "Eye?"</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-The Eye of the Universe.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:14.575 --> 00:14:14.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The tunnel.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:14:15.543 --> 00:14:17.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think she means the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:14:18.281 --> 00:14:21.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are on the other side.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They don't realize we found the Eye.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:14:22.621 --> 00:14:24.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many people are we talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:14:24.861 --> 00:14:27.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Many... three </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>jeetaka.</i></c.bg_transparent>

217
00:14:27.820 --> 00:14:30.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three hundred? Three thousand?</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:14:31.498 --> 00:14:33.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three million?</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:14:34.138 --> 00:14:35.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three million.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:14:35.378 --> 00:14:37.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three million of my people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are on the other side.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:38.437 --> 00:14:41.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We must bring them through the Eye.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We must bring them here.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:56.432 --> 00:14:58.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--Is there anything wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:58.911 --> 00:15:01.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm just not used to the men being here.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:15:01.492 --> 00:15:04.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Skrreean men don't involve themselves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in situations like this.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:15:05.010 --> 00:15:06.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are all your leaders women?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:15:07.250 --> 00:15:10.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-All of them?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You heard her, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:15:10.193 --> 00:15:12.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Men are far too emotional to be leaders.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:15:12.022 --> 00:15:14.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're constantly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>fighting among themselves.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:15:14.932 --> 00:15:16.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's their favorite thing to do.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:15:18.624 --> 00:15:21.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I hope I haven't offended anyone.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:15:24.422 --> 00:15:25.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorry to keep you waiting.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:15:25.782 --> 00:15:27.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek was just telling us</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:15:27.981 --> 00:15:30.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>how the Skrreea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are a female-dominant society.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:15:30.740 --> 00:15:33.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems the men</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are a bit too emotional to be leaders.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:15:34.258 --> 00:15:37.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please do not misunderstand.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We love our men.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:15:39.120 --> 00:15:39.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:15:42.317 --> 00:15:44.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you one of the leaders</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your people, Haneek?</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:15:44.437 --> 00:15:46.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me? Oh, no.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:15:47.376 --> 00:15:50.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm little more than a farmer.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was just lucky.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:15:51.695 --> 00:15:52.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How so?</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:15:52.835 --> 00:15:55.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first one to find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Eye of the Universe.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:15:56.793 --> 00:15:58.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were looking for the wormhole?</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:15:58.453 --> 00:16:00.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had heard about a great</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tunnel being discovered.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:16:01.211 --> 00:16:04.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We knew it must be the Eye of the Universe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that would lead us to Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:16:05.249 --> 00:16:06.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna?</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:16:07.438 --> 00:16:09.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna is the legendary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>home of the Skrreeans.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:16:10.208 --> 00:16:12.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It has always been portrayed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in our sacred texts</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:16:12.789 --> 00:16:15.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as being just beyond</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Eye of the Universe.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:16:15.928 --> 00:16:19.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A planet of sorrow, where the Skrreean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will sow seeds of joy.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:16:20.406 --> 00:16:22.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't guarantee you'll find Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:16:22.985 --> 00:16:25.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I can promise you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that we'll help you find a home.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:16:26.544 --> 00:16:27.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We sent our runabouts</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:16:27.404 --> 00:16:29.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to the Gamma Quadrant</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to make contact with your ships.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:16:30.523 --> 00:16:31.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That will be difficult.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:16:32.135 --> 00:16:34.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're all spread</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out looking for the Eye.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:16:34.942 --> 00:16:39.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And when we find them, what then?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>This station only holds 7,000 people.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:16:39.885 --> 00:16:42.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're talking about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three million Skrreeans.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:16:43.799 --> 00:16:47.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid most of your people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will have to be confined to their ships.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:47.338 --> 00:16:49.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I understand.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-In the meantime,</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:49.945 --> 00:16:51.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>is there any one person</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we should be looking for?</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:52.517 --> 00:16:53.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A leader or leaders?</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:54.756 --> 00:16:57.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Most of our leaders</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were killed by the T-Rogorans.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:57.635 --> 00:16:59.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The T-Rogorans. Who are they?</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:59.655 --> 00:17:02.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For eight centuries,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my people have lived under their rule.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:17:02.593 --> 00:17:05.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have been forced to work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as laborers and servants.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:17:05.692 --> 00:17:08.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were able to escape when the T-Rogorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were invaded and conquered.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:17:09.372 --> 00:17:10.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who conquered them?</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:17:10.751 --> 00:17:11.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I do not know their name.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:17:12.691 --> 00:17:16.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I only know they were members</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of something called "The Dominion."</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:17:22.208 --> 00:17:23.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:17:26.825 --> 00:17:27.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:17:33.065 --> 00:17:35.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did I wake you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, that's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:17:35.483 --> 00:17:38.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, come in. Computer, lights on full.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:17:38.663 --> 00:17:39.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I can come back.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:17:40.961 --> 00:17:45.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been so kind to me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>How could I possibly refuse your company?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:17:50.558 --> 00:17:52.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go back to bed.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Go on! Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:17:53.608 --> 00:17:54.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll join you again after I'm through.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:18:00.363 --> 00:18:01.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are those your husbands?</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:18:02.296 --> 00:18:03.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hus-bands?</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:18:04.455 --> 00:18:07.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not familiar with that word.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're bonded to me.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:18:09.133 --> 00:18:11.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you sleep with them both?</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:18:12.213 --> 00:18:14.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you sleep with your males?</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:18:14.592 --> 00:18:16.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I don't have any males.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:18:18.751 --> 00:18:20.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at the moment, anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:18:21.750 --> 00:18:22.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're very useful.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:18:23.829 --> 00:18:25.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, I can imagine they are.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:18:27.068 --> 00:18:29.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just wanted to tell you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we found some of your ships.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:18:30.207 --> 00:18:32.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Several hundred Skrreeans should</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>be arriving at the station today.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:18:32.999 --> 00:18:34.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We thought it would be a good idea</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:18:35.049 --> 00:18:36.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>if you were there to greet them.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:18:36.984 --> 00:18:37.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why me?</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:18:38.864 --> 00:18:41.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You yourself said most</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your leaders were dead.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:18:42.264 --> 00:18:45.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, that's true, but, Kira,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm just a farmer.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:46.137 --> 00:18:48.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You also were the first one</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through the Eye of the Universe.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:48.300 --> 00:18:52.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's got to mean something...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in some symbolic, sort of way.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:18:52.819 --> 00:18:53.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:18:55.179 --> 00:18:57.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, here.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:18:58.098 --> 00:19:00.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I brought you something.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, open it.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:19:06.517 --> 00:19:07.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seemed to like it.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:19:13.554 --> 00:19:14.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:19:15.554 --> 00:19:18.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you misunderstood.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:19:19.312 --> 00:19:19.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:19:21.332 --> 00:19:24.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought this was the most</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hideous thing I'd ever seen.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:19:26.850 --> 00:19:28.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that makes two of us.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:19:30.949 --> 00:19:33.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's awful.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's horrible.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:19:35.628 --> 00:19:36.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who would wear that?</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:19:51.303 --> 00:19:52.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>JAKE: It was no big deal.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:19:52.783 --> 00:19:55.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>NOG: You go on a date</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a dabo girl for the first time</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:19:55.862 --> 00:19:58.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and you sit there and tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it was no big deal?</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:58.301 --> 00:19:59.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't really a date.</c.bg_transparent>

311
