<c.bg_transparent>I told him I had to help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone with her homework.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:20:06.768 --> 00:20:07.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:20:08.448 --> 00:20:10.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Too bad I'll never</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>be able to use that lie.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:20:10.436 --> 00:20:13.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-My dad knows I never do homework.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not a lie, Nog.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:20:13.644 --> 00:20:15.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mardah's studying entomology.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>She asked me to help her out.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:20:16.515 --> 00:20:19.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A dabo girl who studies entomology?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ha! Sure.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:20:20.221 --> 00:20:20.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's true.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:20:21.211 --> 00:20:21.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:20:25.432 --> 00:20:26.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is entomology?</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:20:27.311 --> 00:20:28.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The study of bugs.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:20:28.791 --> 00:20:30.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you mean she wants to be a chef?</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:20:34.180 --> 00:20:34.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, who's that?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:20:35.229 --> 00:20:36.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>NOG: I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:20:38.889 --> 00:20:42.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's he doing? Oh, that's disgusting!</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:20:42.968 --> 00:20:46.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He must be one of those Skrreeans.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>My dad says there's a lot more on the way.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:20:49.606 --> 00:20:50.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi!</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:20:52.764 --> 00:20:54.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doesn't he know what a replicator's for?</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:20:55.164 --> 00:20:55.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Idiot!</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:20:57.043 --> 00:21:00.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, does Mardah</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have any sisters?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:21:06.200 --> 00:21:08.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'BRIEN: Commander</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've cleared the Skrreean ship</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:21:08.060 --> 00:21:09.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
