345
00:22:48.241 --> 00:22:49.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nog!</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:22:43.980 --> 00:22:46.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know there's no running</c.bg_transparent>
