347
00:22:46.740 --> 00:22:47.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who's running?</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:22:47.600 --> 00:22:51.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What seems to be the problem here?</c.bg_transparent>
