349
00:22:51.660 --> 00:22:53.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ask him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Me?</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:22:53.680 --> 00:22:55.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're the one who stinks.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:22:55.120 --> 00:22:57.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's because you sprayed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that vapor on us.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:22:57.460 --> 00:22:58.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that true, Nog?</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:22:59.240 --> 00:22:59.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:23:01.620 --> 00:23:02.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nog...</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:23:03.519 --> 00:23:04.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a joke.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:23:06.100 --> 00:23:07.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very amusing.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:23:08.220 --> 00:23:10.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you for bringing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this to my attention.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:23:10.019 --> 00:23:11.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll take care of it from here.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:23:12.079 --> 00:23:12.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( squealing )</c.bg_transparent>

360
