361
00:23:18.962 --> 00:23:19.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:23:19.500 --> 00:23:20.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( growling )</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:23:23.300 --> 00:23:24.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
