367
00:23:44.633 --> 00:23:47.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Weapon sales, huh? Very profitable.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:23:47.752 --> 00:23:51.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How would you know about that?</c.bg_transparent>
