369
00:23:52.270 --> 00:23:56.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what would your Uncle Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>know about illegal weapon sales?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:23:57.229 --> 00:23:59.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He, uh... he, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:23:59.629 --> 00:24:03.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Knows better than to ever</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>get involved in anything so disreputable.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:24:03.827 --> 00:24:04.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: I'm sure.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:24:05.607 --> 00:24:08.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the boy's father come to see me.</c.bg_transparent>

374
