<c.bg_transparent>Rom is doing the weekly stock inventory.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to interrupt him.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:24:12.585 --> 00:24:16.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
