379
00:24:25.941 --> 00:24:27.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( laughing nervously )</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:24:28.378 --> 00:24:29.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you have to say for yourself?</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:24:30.699 --> 00:24:32.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--I'm sorry?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:24:32.139 --> 00:24:34.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
