383
00:24:34.518 --> 00:24:38.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That doesn't excuse his actions.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And he will be punished severely.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:24:39.076 --> 00:24:40.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will?</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:24:40.796 --> 00:24:45.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to tell the Constable here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you will never do it again.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:24:46.195 --> 00:24:46.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:24:48.274 --> 00:24:51.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, I won't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I promise. Never again.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:24:51.793 --> 00:24:52.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See that you don't.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:24:54.552 --> 00:24:55.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I leave now?</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:24:58.671 --> 00:25:00.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:25:04.029 --> 00:25:06.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, you really can't blame the boy.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:25:06.588 --> 00:25:08.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And why is that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, come on, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:25:09.307 --> 00:25:11.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know these Skrreeans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are nothing but trouble.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:25:11.647 --> 00:25:12.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're all over the station</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:25:13.386 --> 00:25:16.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>looking and touching,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never buying anything.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:25:17.225 --> 00:25:19.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And they flake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I didn't notice.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:25:20.044 --> 00:25:23.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come to my place.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You'll see little pieces of Skrreean skin</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:25:23.086 --> 00:25:26.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>all over the bar and the floor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's disgusting.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:25:26.646 --> 00:25:28.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Well, they won't be here long.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I hope not.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:25:28.684 --> 00:25:30.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're driving my paying customers away.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:25:31.321 --> 00:25:33.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They stay here too long,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'll be out of business.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:25:33.660 --> 00:25:36.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In that case,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I hope they never leave.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:25:41.817 --> 00:25:43.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:25:43.257 --> 00:25:44.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( excited chatter )</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:25:44.937 --> 00:25:47.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( wind instrument playing softly )</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:25:55.413 --> 00:26:01.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've talked it over among ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Our feelings were unanimous.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:26:02.312 --> 00:26:05.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You discovered the Eye of the Universe.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:26:05.971 --> 00:26:10.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must lead us the rest of the way.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:26:16.647 --> 00:26:18.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do the best I can.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:26:30.763 --> 00:26:31.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That looked serious.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:26:33.843 --> 00:26:35.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is everything all right?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:26:37.401 --> 00:26:38.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look at them.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:26:40.161 --> 00:26:41.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look at my people.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:26:43.371 --> 00:26:45.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never seen them so happy</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:26:46.818 --> 00:26:49.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and here I sit, feeling trapped.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:26:50.657 --> 00:26:51.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:26:51.677 --> 00:26:54.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They expect me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to lead them to Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:26:55.316 --> 00:26:57.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( music ends, crowd applauds)</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:26:57.535 --> 00:26:58.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be okay.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:26:59.655 --> 00:27:03.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Sisko is doing everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he can to find you a place to live.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:27:04.374 --> 00:27:05.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not alone.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:27:05.833 --> 00:27:07.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope I'm not intruding.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:27:07.334 --> 00:27:08.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:27:09.054 --> 00:27:13.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, this is Varani, a great musician.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe the greatest Bajor has ever known.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:27:14.291 --> 00:27:17.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She exaggerates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but that's why I'm so fond of her.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:27:20.228 --> 00:27:21.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being a Bajoran</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:27:21.988 --> 00:27:24.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what it's like to be displaced.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:27:26.247 --> 00:27:27.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a token of friendship</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:27:29.006 --> 00:27:30.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would like to give you this.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:27:33.899 --> 00:27:36.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( playing quiet melody )</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:27:37.384 --> 00:27:42.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's from a concert I played</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>many years ago at the Jalanda Forum.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:27:58.209 --> 00:27:59.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Tumak, where have you been?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Nowhere.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:27:59.457 --> 00:28:01.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-To wash.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:28:12.053 --> 00:28:12.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer...</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:28:14.312 --> 00:28:16.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please show me a chart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this star system.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:28:25.869 --> 00:28:27.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-So, what'd your dad say?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-About what?</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:28:28.028 --> 00:28:29.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>About you getting in trouble with Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:28:29.548 --> 00:28:31.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He was very angry.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He was?</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:28:31.587 --> 00:28:33.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He always gets angry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when I get caught.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:28:37.165 --> 00:28:39.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping ) I just remembered.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have some errands to run for my uncle.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:28:40.262 --> 00:28:41.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going to have to face them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sooner or later.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:28:42.644 --> 00:28:44.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was very funny, what you did.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:28:45.623 --> 00:28:48.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, Jake?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There's a man with a sense of humor.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:28:50.182 --> 00:28:51.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nobody's laughing.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:28:51.941 --> 00:28:53.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And luckily nobody got hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:28:53.841 --> 00:28:55.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think my friend's real sorry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for what he did.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:28:57.690 --> 00:28:58.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aren't you?</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:29:00.499 --> 00:29:01.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:29:02.498 --> 00:29:03.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See? What'd I tell you?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:29:04.097 --> 00:29:05.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't sound sorry to me.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:29:10.611 --> 00:29:11.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( squealing )</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:29:20.532 --> 00:29:22.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:29:23.052 --> 00:29:27.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's enough. Break it up.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I said, break it up!</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:29:29.930 --> 00:29:31.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( snarling )</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:29:31.249 --> 00:29:32.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( growls )</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:29:32.769 --> 00:29:35.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's bad enough you're all hanging</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the station</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:29:35.390 --> 00:29:37.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>without buying anything.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have to start fighting, too?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:29:38.407 --> 00:29:40.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought we were welcome here.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:29:40.526 --> 00:29:42.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, make yourself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>welcome somewhere else.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:29:44.468 --> 00:29:45.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want us here.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:29:45.876 --> 00:29:47.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want anything to do with us.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:29:47.612 --> 00:29:49.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, we don't want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anything to do with you.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:29:51.330 --> 00:29:52.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any of you!</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:29:52.885 --> 00:29:53.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>yells </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:29:53.969 --> 00:29:54.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>hisses </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:29:57.609 --> 00:29:59.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: I can see the Skrreeans</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:29:59.168 --> 00:30:01.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>don't bother to teach</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their children manners.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:30:01.407 --> 00:30:02.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>hisses </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:30:04.660 --> 00:30:07.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Dax and I have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>combing through data on every uninhabited</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:30:07.119 --> 00:30:08.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>M-Class planet in the sector.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:08.758 --> 00:30:09.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We think that Draylon II</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:09.636 --> 00:30:10.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>would make a perfect home</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Skrreea.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:30:12.676 --> 00:30:14.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Draylon II? I've never heard of it.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:30:15.796 --> 00:30:18.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's near Sefalla Prime.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's got definite possibilities.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:30:18.995 --> 00:30:22.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stable orbit, temperate climate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a very low surface radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:30:23.474 --> 00:30:25.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Add to that good soil</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a long growing season.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:30:26.512 --> 00:30:27.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's our best bet.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:30:31.831 --> 00:30:33.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:30:40.020 --> 00:30:40.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-May we come in?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:30:50.345 --> 00:30:51.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ladies.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:30:54.165 --> 00:30:57.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive them, Commander Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They don't mean any disrespect.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:30:58.223 --> 00:30:58.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:30:59.503 --> 00:31:02.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have some encouraging news.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We think we've found a planet</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:31:02.745 --> 00:31:05.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for you and your people,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one with excellent potential</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:31:05.295 --> 00:31:06.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for resettlement.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:31:09.120 --> 00:31:14.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We appreciate all your hard work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm afraid it was unnecessary.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:31:14.538 --> 00:31:16.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, we found Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:31:17.957 --> 00:31:18.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did?</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:31:19.216 --> 00:31:21.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A planet of sorrow, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:31:23.179 --> 00:31:27.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna is your planet.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna is Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:31:36.735 --> 00:31:39.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, Stardate 47391.2.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:31:40.290 --> 00:31:42.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chief O'Brien is continuing</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to oversee repairs</i></c.bg_transparent>

493
00:31:42.551 --> 00:31:44.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Skrreean ships docked</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>at the station.</i></c.bg_transparent>

494
00:31:44.549 --> 00:31:47.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Meanwhile, Minister Rozahn</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and Vedek Sorad have arrived</i></c.bg_transparent>

495
00:31:47.551 --> 00:31:50.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>from Bajor with an official response</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Skrreeans' request to immigrate.</i></c.bg_transparent>

496
00:31:51.789 --> 00:31:54.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Major, if I may have a moment?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm sorry, Varani.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:31:54.549 --> 00:31:56.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm on my way to a meeting.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:31:56.148 --> 00:31:58.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, with Minister Rozahn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Vedek Sorad.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:31:59.445 --> 00:32:02.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I presume Haneek will be there as well.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:32:02.445 --> 00:32:05.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please tell here that my heart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>goes out to her and her people.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:32:05.324 --> 00:32:09.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell her how much Bajorans everywhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>regret having to refuse their request.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:32:09.286 --> 00:32:12.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Aren't you being a little premature?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Am I? You know what</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:32:12.076 --> 00:32:14.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the provisional government's answer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is going to be.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:32:14.235 --> 00:32:16.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>These are people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who have lost everything, Varani.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:32:17.379 --> 00:32:20.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, and I wish there was some way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we could help them.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:32:21.898 --> 00:32:26.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Bajor is in shambles, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that as well as I do.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:32:29.995 --> 00:32:32.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>First of all, I want you all to know</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:32:32.156 --> 00:32:35.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the provisional government</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has taken the Skrreeans' request</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:32:35.081 --> 00:32:37.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for immigration very seriously.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:32:38.753 --> 00:32:42.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The debate in the Chamber of Ministers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>became quite heated at times.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:32:43.132 --> 00:32:45.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Though I suppose you could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>say that about all of our debates.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:32:46.011 --> 00:32:47.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But a decision was reached?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:32:47.730 --> 00:32:50.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, I was sent here to tell you</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:32:50.929 --> 00:32:53.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the Ministers, in accord</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Vedek Assembly,</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:32:53.928 --> 00:32:56.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have decided</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to deny the Skrreeans' request.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:32:57.809 --> 00:32:58.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ROZAHN: I am sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:32:59.107 --> 00:33:02.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor simply cannot absorb</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three million refugees</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:33:02.709 --> 00:33:03.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>at this time.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:33:04.027 --> 00:33:06.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After what the Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>did to our planet</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:33:06.505 --> 00:33:08.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we can barely take care of our own.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:33:08.464 --> 00:33:10.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But no one is asking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you to take care of us.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:33:11.343 --> 00:33:12.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This decision is not based</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:33:13.882 --> 00:33:15.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>strictly on Bajoran self-interest.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:33:16.642 --> 00:33:18.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such a huge increase in population</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:33:18.863 --> 00:33:21.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>would prove to be tragic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your people as well as ours.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:33:21.661 --> 00:33:23.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Bajor has more than enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>room for us.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:33:24.000 --> 00:33:27.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The plains of the Northwest Peninsula</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are practically uninhabited.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:33:27.182 --> 00:33:28.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The land's ideal for farming.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:33:29.020 --> 00:33:30.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It used to be</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:30.938 --> 00:33:32.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>before the Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>got their hands on it.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:33.737 --> 00:33:36.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Minister Rozahn,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Skrreea are farmers.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:37.115 --> 00:33:38.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just give us the land.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:33:38.776 --> 00:33:41.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guarantee you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can make it thrive again.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:33:41.454 --> 00:33:44.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Under ideal circumstances,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>perhaps you could.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:33:44.953 --> 00:33:47.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But what if the circumstances</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aren't ideal?</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:33:48.313 --> 00:33:49.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if we go through</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another long winter?</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:50.432 --> 00:33:51.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if your crops fail?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:52.511 --> 00:33:53.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if the famine</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:33:53.491 --> 00:33:55.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that has been plaguing Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>continues to spread?</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:33:56.430 --> 00:33:56.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What then?</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:33:58.070 --> 00:33:59.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are willing to take that risk.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:33:59.711 --> 00:34:01.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ROZAHN: I'm afraid we aren't.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:34:01.688 --> 00:34:03.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ran a series of projections</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:34:03.269 --> 00:34:05.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to see whether a Skrreean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>settlement could survive</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:34:05.399 --> 00:34:06.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the Northwest peninsula.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:34:07.486 --> 00:34:09.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The results were not encouraging.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:34:10.686 --> 00:34:11.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Haneek?</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:34:11.945 --> 00:34:13.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you should seriously consider</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:13.625 --> 00:34:15.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Draylon II as an alternate to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:15.664 --> 00:34:18.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The winters are mild.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There's plenty of good farmland.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:18.632 --> 00:34:21.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! Projections can be wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:34:21.385 --> 00:34:23.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SORAD: But what if they're not?</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:34:23.902 --> 00:34:27.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is Bajor to do if your people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>start dying?</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:34:27.441 --> 00:34:30.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought I made that clear.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We are not expecting your help.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:34:30.919 --> 00:34:33.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you really think we could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>stand by and do nothing?</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:34:34.078 --> 00:34:37.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We would feel obligated to help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with food, with clothing</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:34:37.800 --> 00:34:40.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-with whatever it would take.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And where would that aid come from?</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:34:41.398 --> 00:34:43.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SORAD: Our resources are already depleted.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:34:43.916 --> 00:34:46.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To help you would mean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>depriving our own people.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:34:47.834 --> 00:34:50.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am afraid the decision</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the provisional government is final.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:34:52.073 --> 00:34:54.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreea will have to find somewhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>else to live.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:34:57.032 --> 00:34:59.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, talk to them.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:35:00.721 --> 00:35:01.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell them they're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:35:03.750 --> 00:35:04.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Help us.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:35:08.688 --> 00:35:09.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:35:11.808 --> 00:35:12.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, Haneek...</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:35:14.522 --> 00:35:15.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But they're right. I wish they weren't.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:35:16.606 --> 00:35:18.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish Bajor was Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:35:20.585 --> 00:35:21.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it's not.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:35:25.024 --> 00:35:26.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's still Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:35:37.500 --> 00:35:38.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:35:38.899 --> 00:35:39.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look at this!</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:35:45.497 --> 00:35:46.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:35:48.577 --> 00:35:50.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you like cake</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the icoberry torte is really good.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:35:51.556 --> 00:35:53.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that big-eared troll</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>really your friend?</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:35:53.715 --> 00:35:55.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He's an idiot.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:35:55.895 --> 00:35:57.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not the first to say that.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:35:57.593 --> 00:35:59.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he's not such a bad guy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>once you get to know him.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:36:00.593 --> 00:36:02.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't plan on being</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around here that long.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:36:03.432 --> 00:36:05.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My dad says you're probably</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>going to Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:36:05.711 --> 00:36:06.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Does he?</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:36:07.091 --> 00:36:08.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, sounds like a nice place.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:36:09.210 --> 00:36:10.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you want to move there?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:36:10.650 --> 00:36:11.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:36:12.506 --> 00:36:13.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither do I.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:36:19.527 --> 00:36:21.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:36:21.526 --> 00:36:22.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:36:29.804 --> 00:36:31.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek...</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:36:33.645 --> 00:36:36.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The thing I don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is why you pretended</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:36:36.004 --> 00:36:36.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:36:37.922 --> 00:36:39.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wasn't pretending.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:36:40.280 --> 00:36:41.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah!</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:36:41.081 --> 00:36:42.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you are my friend...</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:36:43.639 --> 00:36:44.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until I need you.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:36:49.758 --> 00:36:53.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know it's hard for you to see right now</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I am trying to help.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:36:53.717 --> 00:36:55.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think I've had quite enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your help.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:36:56.347 --> 00:36:57.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got to believe me.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:36:57.276 --> 00:36:59.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Sisko has found</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you a wonderful home.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:37:00.854 --> 00:37:02.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You betrayed me, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:37:03.014 --> 00:37:04.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:37:05.153 --> 00:37:07.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I honestly believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the provisional government</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:37:07.214 --> 00:37:08.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>made the right decision</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:37:08.372 --> 00:37:09.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>both for Bajor and the Skrreeans.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:37:10.851 --> 00:37:13.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If that's true,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have nothing more to discuss.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:37:17.549 --> 00:37:19.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping we could still be friends.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:37:20.429 --> 00:37:23.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So in other words, you came here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>looking for forgiveness.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:37:25.741 --> 00:37:26.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I don't forgive you.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:37:29.693 --> 00:37:30.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sisko to Kira.</i></c.bg_transparent>

609
00:37:31.906 --> 00:37:32.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:37:33.005 --> 00:37:33.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Is Haneek with you?</i></c.bg_transparent>

611
00:37:34.324 --> 00:37:35.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:37:35.626 --> 00:37:38.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I need both of you in Ops immediately.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tumak has taken a ship.</i></c.bg_transparent>

613
00:37:38.703 --> 00:37:39.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>He's headed for Bajor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

614
00:37:57.378 --> 00:37:59.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-They're not responding, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Keep trying, Mr. O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:37:59.657 --> 00:38:00.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did this happen?</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:38:01.217 --> 00:38:02.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>With all the traffic around the station</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:38:02.878 --> 00:38:04.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak and two of his friends</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were able to slip away.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:38:05.055 --> 00:38:07.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We didn't even know the ship was gone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until the Bajorans contacted us.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:38:09.011 --> 00:38:10.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, I need for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to try to talk to your son.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:38:11.142 --> 00:38:13.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a high-energy radiation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>leak in the port nacelle.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:38:13.942 --> 00:38:16.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've tried to make him aware of it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he refuses to acknowledge us.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:38:16.661 --> 00:38:19.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, open a channel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Skrreean vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:38:19.380 --> 00:38:20.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:38:22.619 --> 00:38:23.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ready.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:38:26.698 --> 00:38:27.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak?</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:38:29.497 --> 00:38:30.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Listen to me.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:38:32.647 --> 00:38:33.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your ship's in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:38:35.548 --> 00:38:37.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( quietly ) Have him turn off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>his engines and drift</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:38:37.648 --> 00:38:39.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>until the Bajorans can tractor him in.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:38:40.367 --> 00:38:43.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, turn off your engines.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:38:43.925 --> 00:38:47.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must turn your engines off, now!</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:38:49.052 --> 00:38:49.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not responding.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:38:51.312 --> 00:38:53.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, this is serious!</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:38:53.022 --> 00:38:54.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your life is in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:38:54.560 --> 00:38:57.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The others who are with you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their lives are in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:38:57.021 --> 00:38:59.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please! Answer me!</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:39:00.382 --> 00:39:00.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( console beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:39:01.295 --> 00:39:04.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sensors are detecting two Bajoran vessels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>closing in on the Skrreean ship.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:39:04.775 --> 00:39:08.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Display it here. Mr. O'Brien,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>patch us into the Bajoran interceptor.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:39:08.936 --> 00:39:09.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'BRIEN: Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:39:10.016 --> 00:39:11.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>BAJORAN: Entered restricted space.</i></c.bg_transparent>

642
00:39:11.775 --> 00:39:13.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You must turn around</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and leave immediately.</i></c.bg_transparent>

643
00:39:13.755 --> 00:39:14.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a channel.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:39:14.975 --> 00:39:17.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Major Kira</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Nerys on Deep Space 9.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:39:17.548 --> 00:39:19.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreean vessel has refused</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to acknowledge our hails.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:39:19.973 --> 00:39:22.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Communications may be down.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have to let them land.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:39:22.412 --> 00:39:24.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>That's impossible, Major.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>We have strict orders</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>not to allow</i></c.bg_transparent>

648
00:39:24.893 --> 00:39:26.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>any Skrreean vessel to land.</i></c.bg_transparent>

649
00:39:26.610 --> 00:39:27.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pilot's just a boy.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:39:27.811 --> 00:39:30.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He took the ship without permission.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's barely operational.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:39:30.673 --> 00:39:32.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: We're not even sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'll make it back here.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:39:32.868 --> 00:39:34.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm sorry, Major, but we have our orders.</i></c.bg_transparent>

653
00:39:34.272 --> 00:39:35.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who gave you those orders?</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:39:35.428 --> 00:39:36.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They come directly from General Hazar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

655
00:39:37.148 --> 00:39:39.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax, get me General Hazar on Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:39:39.505 --> 00:39:42.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell his people it's an emergency.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want to speak to him now.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:39:42.606 --> 00:39:43.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by, interceptor.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:39:43.626 --> 00:39:45.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>General Hazar will be countermanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>those orders any minute.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:39:46.705 --> 00:39:48.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The interceptor is closing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the Skrreean ship.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:39:51.943 --> 00:39:53.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's General Hazar, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:39:53.903 --> 00:39:54.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:39:54.943 --> 00:39:57.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>What is this about, Commander?</i></c.bg_transparent>

663
00:39:57.262 --> 00:39:59.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's about the Skrreean vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's approaching Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:39:59.701 --> 00:40:01.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've already given the orders</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to have it turned back.</i></c.bg_transparent>

665
00:40:02.181 --> 00:40:05.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That ship is being flown by a child</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it's leaking radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:40:06.019 --> 00:40:06.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>A child?</i></c.bg_transparent>

667
00:40:07.059 --> 00:40:08.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PILOT: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Skrreean ship. Repeating.</i></c.bg_transparent>

668
00:40:08.735 --> 00:40:12.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Return to the space station now.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Have him shut down his engines.</i></c.bg_transparent>

669
00:40:12.237 --> 00:40:13.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll tow him back.</i></c.bg_transparent>

670
00:40:13.797 --> 00:40:17.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, please, turn your engines off.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:40:17.715 --> 00:40:18.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( shots firing )</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:40:19.035 --> 00:40:20.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interceptor One, what's going on?</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:40:20.475 --> 00:40:22.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They've opened fire on us.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Taking evasive action.</i></c.bg_transparent>

674
00:40:22.085 --> 00:40:23.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, don't do this!</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:40:23.564 --> 00:40:25.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>PILOT: We've been hit!</i></c.bg_transparent>

676
00:40:25.953 --> 00:40:27.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, they're returning fire.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:40:27.513 --> 00:40:28.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:40:28.312 --> 00:40:31.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Disengage, interceptor! Repeat, disengage.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:40:30.950 --> 00:40:33.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>General, tell your pilots</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to hold their fire.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:40:35.242 --> 00:40:36.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relaying that order now.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:40:41.639 --> 00:40:42.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sobs )</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:40:44.879 --> 00:40:46.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interceptor One.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:40:47.038 --> 00:40:50.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The Skrreean ship exploded.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I didn't even think we hit it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

684
00:40:51.397 --> 00:40:53.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The phaser beam must've ignited</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the radiation leak.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:40:56.664 --> 00:40:58.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm very sorry, Commander.</i></c.bg_transparent>

686
00:40:59.503 --> 00:41:01.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all are, General.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:41:33.573 --> 00:41:36.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just stopped by to wish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you luck on Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:41:37.325 --> 00:41:40.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, I still believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this is the best choice...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:41:40.745 --> 00:41:42.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For Bajor and for you.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:41:43.050 --> 00:41:45.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You still believe we would have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a burden to your people?</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:41:47.728 --> 00:41:48.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:41:49.481 --> 00:41:51.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you've made a terrible mistake.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:41:52.187 --> 00:41:52.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of you.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:41:53.727 --> 00:41:54.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we could have helped you.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:41:55.746 --> 00:41:57.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we could have helped each other.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:41:58.165 --> 00:42:02.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreeans are farmers, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have a famine on your planet.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:42:03.084 --> 00:42:05.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps we could have made</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that peninsula bloom again.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:42:06.854 --> 00:42:07.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HANEEK: We'll never know, will we?</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:42:09.142 --> 00:42:11.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fifty years of Cardassian rule</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:42:11.163 --> 00:42:14.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have made you all frightened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and suspicious.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:42:15.921 --> 00:42:17.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel sorry for you.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:42:22.898 --> 00:42:23.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were right.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:42:24.997 --> 00:42:26.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor is not Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

